## Common Patterns

### 1. Service Initialization
```swift
class MyService: ObservableObject {
    let modelContainer: ModelContainer
    let modelContext: ModelContext

    init(modelContainer: ModelContainer, modelContext: ModelContext) {
        self.modelContainer = modelContainer
        self.modelContext = modelContext
    }
}
```

### 2. Async Service Operations
```swift
func performAsyncOperation() async throws -> Result {
    return try await Task {
        // Async operation
    }.value
}
```

### 3. Error Handling
```swift
do {
    let result = try await service.performOperation()
    // Handle success
} catch {
    // Handle error gracefully
    // Show user-friendly message
    // Log error for debugging
}
```

These rules ensure consistent, well-architected service development in the Ora Browser codebase.